title: Cajun-Style Wings & Kale Salad Kale yeah! | 2 Servings
description: Is there anything more craveable than chicken wings? Answer: Chicken wings and a kale salad! The wings are coated in a savory blend of kickin’ Cajun spices and are crispy on the outside and super-juicy on the inside. They pair perfectly with a crunchy salad that’s positively bursting with kale, green cabbage, broccoli, Brussels sprouts, chicory, roasted pumpkin seeds, and dried cranberries, all tossed in a savory-sweet poppy seed dressing.

